subject: Baseball
World Series
Ratings and Rating Systems
Television
lead_paragraph: The San Francisco Giants’ victory in Game 5 of the World Series on Monday night was seen by an average of 15 million viewers, down 11 percent from the 16.9 million for last year’s comparable game between the Yankees and the Phillies.
